		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>From flicks to clicks: Mac OS X Trojan Adware.Yontoo infects via fake codec</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Protection and remediation tips for Mac OS X users targeted by a Trojan adware plugin called Yontoo hidden behind movie trailer and other media playing links, generating money for criminals exploiting online ad schemes.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2013-03-22 13:10:52">22 Mar 2013 - 01:10PM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>	

            <div class="content">
                <div class="social-wrapper" id="social-sharer">
                    <span class="text">Share</span>
